      <title>한자 테스트</title>
      <link href="/2019/07/hanja-test/"/>
      <url>/2019/07/hanja-test/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/deed.ko" target="_blank"><img alt="CC BY 4.0" style="border-width:0" src="https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/buttons/80x15/svg/by.svg"></a></p><p>한자 테스트입니다. 접속 환경에 따라 각 나라 자형대로 표시되지 않을 수 있습니다.</p><p>왼쪽에서부터 한국, 일본, 대만, 중국</p><p><span lang="ko">社</span> <span lang="ja">社</span> <span lang="zh-tw">社</span> <span lang="zh-cn">社</span> (모일 사)</p><p><span lang="ko">送</span> <span lang="ja">送</span> <span lang="zh-tw">送</span> <span lang="zh-cn">送</span> (보낼 송)</p><p><span lang="ko">憎</span> <span lang="ja">憎</span> <span lang="zh-tw">憎</span> <span lang="zh-cn">憎</span> (미울 증)</p><p><span lang="ko">著</span> <span lang="ja">著</span> <span lang="zh-tw">著</span> <span lang="zh-cn">著</span> (나타날 저)</p><p><span lang="ko">慨</span> <span lang="ja">慨</span> <span lang="zh-tw">慨</span> <span lang="zh-cn">慨</span> (슬퍼할 개)</p><p><span lang="ko">情</span> <span lang="ja">情</span> <span lang="zh-tw">情</span> <span lang="zh-cn">情</span> (뜻 정)</p><p><span lang="ko">骨</span> <span lang="ja">骨</span> <span lang="zh-tw">骨</span> <span lang="zh-cn">骨</span> (뼈 골)</p><p>이외에도 더 있긴 하지만 생략하겠습니다.</p><h2 id="소스"><a href="#소스" class="headerlink" title="소스"></a>소스</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--모일 사--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ko"</span>&gt;</span>社<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ja"</span>&gt;</span>社<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-tw"</span>&gt;</span>社<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-cn"</span>&gt;</span>社<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--보낼 송--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ko"</span>&gt;</span>送<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ja"</span>&gt;</span>送<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-tw"</span>&gt;</span>送<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-cn"</span>&gt;</span>送<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--미울 증--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ko"</span>&gt;</span>憎<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ja"</span>&gt;</span>憎<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-tw"</span>&gt;</span>憎<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-cn"</span>&gt;</span>憎<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--나타날 저--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ko"</span>&gt;</span>著<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ja"</span>&gt;</span>著<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-tw"</span>&gt;</span>著<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-cn"</span>&gt;</span>著<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--슬퍼할 개--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ko"</span>&gt;</span>慨<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ja"</span>&gt;</span>慨<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-tw"</span>&gt;</span>慨<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-cn"</span>&gt;</span>慨<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--뜻 정--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ko"</span>&gt;</span>情<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ja"</span>&gt;</span>情<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-tw"</span>&gt;</span>情<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-cn"</span>&gt;</span>情<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--뼈 골--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ko"</span>&gt;</span>骨<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"ja"</span>&gt;</span>骨<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-tw"</span>&gt;</span>骨<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh-cn"</span>&gt;</span>骨<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="참고할만한-사이트"><a href="#참고할만한-사이트" class="headerlink" title="참고할만한 사이트"></a>참고할만한 사이트</h2><p><a href="http://ko.glyphwiki.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">글리프위키</a> - 한자 자형을 정리해놓은 사이트입니다.</p>]]></content>
      
      
